## Local Development .env\n# 1. Create FREE MongoDB Atlas account: https://www.mongodb.com/atlas\n# 2. Create cluster, add IP 0.0.0.0/0, get connect string\n\nMONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://<username>:<password>@cluster0.xxxxx.mongodb.net/restaurant?retryWrites=true&amp;w=majority\n\nJWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_jwt_key_change_this\nPORT=5001\n\n# Optional Razorpay (test mode)\nRAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzp_test_xxxx\nRAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=xxxx\n\n## Copy from Render .env if exists:\n# MONGODB_URI=...\n# JWT_SECRET=...
